data.description:
Awesome opportunities for financing available with a blended rate of under 5% from our preferred lending partner. Call for details!!
In the highly desirable neighborhood of Surprise Farms, this home boasts 3 beds, 2 baths, formal living room, family room, dining area, and even a den that could be converted to a 4th bedroom. 
No neighbors to the north with a lush greenbelt and large mature trees for your enjoyment and beautifully landscaped front and backyards. Enter through the beautiful new front wooden door into an open floor plan with newly updated LVP flooring throughout the main areas. 
The kitchen has newer stainless steel appliances including refrigerator and 6 burner gas stove! Also in the kitchen are granite countertops and upgraded staggered cabinets!
